```

Key features:
1. Built-in validators (required, minLength, maxLength, email, pattern, min, max, oneOf)
2. Composability via .pipe()
3. Custom validators supported
4. Async validators via async() helper
5. Cross-field validation via .refine()
6. Nested objects and arrays
7. I18n via message keys (not hardcoded strings)
8. Type inference via InferType helper
